{"tid":1368753,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要] 慎防 遍地開花 入面想漂白嘅黑警","createTime":"2019-07-26T14:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T14:26:49.000Z","uid":39085,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5a237eb32e574a0fd9d76910b3f69334404b1bf8","tid":1368753,"uid":39085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:21:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我鄭重同你班黑警講</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔係寫隻字影張相就有用嘅<br />\n<br />\n比啲誠意, 實際行動比香港市民睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係辭職<br />\n<br />\n一係爆料 爆黑警勾結內幕等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你仲留係入面, 唔敢出聲 只係敢影相放上網有咩用?<br />\n班犬就唔會打市民? 佢地就唔會同黑社會勾結?<br />\n你仲留係入面, 唔敢出聲, 代表沉默<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而沉默亦即係幫兇!!!!</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">定係戴定頭盔他日想避免清算?</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家請小心被佢地帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b358f9b509ac4665ef99fa277748f810f1a3a6","tid":1368753,"uid":39085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:21:40.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"02de7b8c1739c6306c13c5845e06c0510103a670","tid":1368753,"uid":39085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7b358f9b509ac4665ef99fa277748f810f1a3a6","tid":1368753,"uid":39085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:21:40.000Z","msg":"光"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:21:50.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"d4325d0980f58287bb744d585d195c779f3536dc","tid":1368753,"uid":39085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02de7b8c1739c6306c13c